#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:386
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select a game difficulty. On higher difficulty levels the walls are build "
"slower while balls move faster. That makes it harder to fence an area in the "
"board."
msgstr ""
"Izberite težavnost igre. Na višjih težavnostnih stopnjah se stene gradijo "
"počasneje, medtem ko se žoge premikajo hitreje. Zaradi tega je težje "
"ograditi območje v plošči."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:393
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Additionally &kbounce; has the common &kde; <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> and "
"<guimenu>Help</guimenu> menu items, for more information read the sections "
"about the <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings"
"\">Settings Menu</ulink> and <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus."
"html#menus-help\">Help Menu</ulink> of the &kde; Fundamentals."
msgstr ""
"Poleg tega &kbounce; ima skupno &kde; Elementi menija <guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu> in <guimenu>Pomoč</guimenu>, za več informacij preberite razdelke o "
"<ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings\">meniju z "
"nastavitvami</ulink> in <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-help"
"\">meni Pomoč</ulink> v &kde; Osnove."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:404
#, no-c-format
msgid "Frequently asked questions"
msgstr "Pogosto zastavljena vprašanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:409
#, no-c-format
msgid "I want to change the way this game looks. Can I?"
msgstr "Želim spremeniti videz te igre. Ali lahko?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:410
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Yes. To change &kbounce; visual theme you can use "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure &kbounce;…</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> option on the menubar."
msgstr ""
"Da. Če želite spremeniti vizualno temo &kbounce; lahko uporabite možnost "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj &kbounce;…"
"</guimenuitem></menuchoice> v menijski vrstici."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:413
#, no-c-format
msgid "I have made a mistake. Can I undo?"
msgstr "Naredil sem napako. Ali jo lahko razveljavim?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:414
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kbounce; does not have an <quote>Undo</quote> feature."
msgstr "&kbounce; nima funkcije <quote>Razveljavi</quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:417
#, no-c-format
msgid "Can I use the keyboard to play this game?"
msgstr "Ali lahko uporabljam tipkovnico za igranje te igre?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:418
#, no-c-format
msgid "No. &kbounce; cannot be played using keyboard."
msgstr "Št. &kbounce; ni mogoče predvajati s tipkovnico."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:421
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"I have to quit the game now, but I am not finished yet. Can I save my "
"progress?"
msgstr ""
"Zdaj moram zapustiti igro, vendar še nisem končal. Ali lahko shranim svoj "
"napredek?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:422
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kbounce; does not have a <quote>Save</quote> feature at the moment."
msgstr "&kbounce; trenutno nima funkcije <quote>Shrani</quote>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:427
#, no-c-format
msgid "Game Configuration"
msgstr "Konfiguracija igre"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:428
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &kbounce; configuration dialog allows you to select visual themes for "
"&kbounce;."
msgstr ""
"&kbounce; konfiguracijsko pogovorno okno vam omogoča izbiro vizualnih tem za "
"&kbounce;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:429
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To select a new theme simply choose the theme from the selection list. Each "
"item in the list shows a small preview left to the theme name. A selection "
"is immediately applied."
msgstr ""
"Če želite izbrati novo temo, preprosto izberite temo na izbirnem seznamu. "
"Vsak element na seznamu prikazuje majhen predogled levo od imena teme. Izbor "
"se uporabi takoj."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:434
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can select random background pictures from a user defined folder with "
"images."
msgstr ""
"Izberete lahko naključne slike ozadja iz uporabniško določene mape s slikami."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:437
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once you are satisfied with the theme you have selected you can click the "
"<guibutton>OK</guibutton> button, located at the bottom part of this dialog."
msgstr ""
"Ko ste zadovoljni z izbrano temo, lahko kliknete gumb <guibutton>V redu</"
"guibutton>, ki se nahaja na dnu tega pogovornega okna."

